<a class="potential-intro-badge" href="/life/potentials/how-powerful-is-the-human-mind"><div class='row'>
<div class='col-md-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-3'>
<i class='fa fa-quote-left fa-4x'></i>
</div>
<div class='col-md-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-9'>
<p>
A group of Asian women were given similar math tests on two separate occasions. The first time around, they were primed to think about the fact that they were women, stereotypically worse at math than men. The second time around, they were told to focus on their identity as Asians, generally thought to be math whizzes compared to other ethnic groups. The result: The women performed far better in the second situation than they did in the first.
</p>
<p>
<small class='pull-right'>The Happiness Advantage</small>
</p>
</div>
</div>
</a><a class="potential-intro-badge" href="/life/potentials/the-definition-of-happiness-in-psychology"><div class='row'>
